readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to perform risk assessment on electronic travel authority (ETA) visa applications.

Service Behaviour

The provider invokes a SV415 service call with the data from the SV556 request. The SV415 response forms part of the SV556 response.

Transformation

Transformation exists on the ESB between external ETAS SV556 and internal enterprise messages.
